
Defining array values in a file :

res/values/arrays.xml

<resources>
    <string-array name="courseDescriptions">
        <item>Android 4.0 includes a number of new developer features. </item>
        <item>This course covers beginning level Android development.</item>
        <item>Virtually all interactivity between Android components occurs.</item>
        <item>The ActionBar incorporates a variety of previously disparate.</item>
        <item>In this course you will learn how to use Android services.</item>
    </string-array>
</resources>



Using array values:

String[] _courseDescriptions;
_courseDescriptions = getResources().getStringArray(R.array.courseDescriptions);
